# KCAA Smart Assistant

A RAG-based chatbot that answers questions about KCAA regulations and aviation information using official documents.

## Features

- Document-based Q&A using RAG
- Source citation
- Real-time processing
- User-friendly interface

## How it Works

1. Uploads PDF documents to create a knowledge base
2. Uses ChromaDB for vector storage
3. Retrieves relevant context for each query
4. Generates accurate answers with citations

docker build --network=host -t kcaa-rag-chatbot .


docker run -d \
  --name kcaa-rag-chatbot \
  -p 8501:8501 \
  --network=host \
  -v $(pwd)/data:/app/data \
  -v $(pwd)/chroma_db:/app/chroma_db \
  kcaa-rag-chatbot